1. SYSTEM OVERVIEW

1.1 Core Identity

· Official Name: Quantum-Edge-Neuromorphic Engine AI Operating System (QUENNE AI OS)
· Version: 2.0.1 (Cognitive Stability Release)
· Architecture Type: Heterogeneous Cognitive Computing Architecture
· Paradigm: Embodied Cognitive Intelligence
· Development Timeline: 2024-2026 (Current: January 2026)

1.2 Foundational Principles

1. Cognitive First: Meaning precedes data processing
2. Uncertainty-Native: Probabilistic reasoning at all layers
3. Continuous Plasticity: Lifelong learning without catastrophic forgetting
4. Embodied Cognition: Intelligence requires sensorimotor engagement
5. Homeostatic Regulation: Biological-like stability mechanisms

